        <Parent_String>perspective views by point of view [300101707], perspective views (visual works) [300034294], images by method of projection [300068504], images by method of representation [300033974], visual works by form of image [300191088], visual works by form [300191087], visual works (works) [300191086], Visual Works (hierarchy name) [300179869], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
